reviewText: I just wanted Robin Hood but got three other movies. Dragon Heart is good but the other 2 we did finish watching: not as good.

Van Damme can act but would make a good truck driver!  After about ten minuets I threw all four in the trash.  Don't know why I purchased them as I knew he was a lousy actor, but hope springs eternal.
The only decent movie among the four is Robin Hood.
AS ADVERTISED, AND EXPECTED. TWO DISKS WITH TWO FULL FEATURE LENGTH MOVIES ON EACH DISK,
Great mix of movies, 2 of which I hadn't seen before love it whish there were more combos in this catagory
Lots of adventure. Nice movies and good price for what you get

Nice to have so many great movies. Only drawback is that with the soon to be end of DVDs to try and get folks to switch to blu ray, there are only 2 discs in this buy, thereby cutting down some time in the films here and there. Mainly in Robin Hood, theres two scenes I feel help to add to the film. Otherwise, good buys.
